long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension sets your default search engine to Yahoo.

Search the web and see status of how many searches you have done.
You can check your status by signing up through Browser action button (extensions puzzle icon at the top right corner).

By clicking "Add To Chrome", you accept and agree to install the SideHustle Plus Extension and set the default search engine to the one provided by the service. The search features within the extension will be provided by Yahoo.
